name: .950 JDJ
description: A powerful large caliber rifle cartridge, yet an exceptionally obscure one. Whatever you shoot with this is probably going to die. This ammo hasn't been produced in over half a decade, you'll have to conserve it if you can't reload it.

name: .950 JDJ casing
description: An empty casing from a .950 JDJ round.  These are incredibly rare, so you might want to hold onto these.
